REM Test script for MEDIA and GLOBE commands
REM This tests the new Consumer HID support (requires ENABLE_CONSUMER)

DEFAULTDELAY 500

REM Test MEDIA commands - Volume controls
LED 255 0 0
MEDIA VOLUMEUP
DELAY 200
MEDIA VOLUMEUP
DELAY 200
MEDIA VOLUMEDOWN
DELAY 500

REM Test MEDIA - Mute
MEDIA MUTE
DELAY 500
MEDIA MUTE
DELAY 500

REM Test MEDIA - Playback controls
LED 0 255 0
MEDIA PLAY
DELAY 1000
MEDIA PAUSE
DELAY 1000
MEDIA NEXT
DELAY 500
MEDIA PREVIOUS
DELAY 500
MEDIA STOP
DELAY 500

REM Test MEDIA - Application launchers
LED 0 0 255
MEDIA CALCULATOR
DELAY 2000
ALT F4
DELAY 500

MEDIA BROWSER
DELAY 2000
ALT F4
DELAY 500

REM Test MEDIA - Browser controls
MEDIA HOME
DELAY 500
MEDIA REFRESH
DELAY 500
MEDIA BACK
DELAY 500
MEDIA FORWARD
DELAY 500

REM Test GLOBE key (if supported on the system)
LED 255 255 0
GLOBE
DELAY 1000

REM Test combinations - GLOBE with other keys
HOLD GLOBE
STRING a
RELEASE
DELAY 200

LED 0 255 0
REM End of test
